




{"id":4875,"date":"2021-02-04T11:13:24","date_gmt":"2021-02-04T04:13:24","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/?p=4875"},"modified":"2022-06-28T13:22:49","modified_gmt":"2022-06-28T06:22:49","slug":"man-hinh-led-tuong-tac-thong-minh-bao-ve-mat-nguoi-dung-nhu-the-nao","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/man-hinh-led-tuong-tac-thong-minh-bao-ve-mat-nguoi-dung-nhu-the-nao\/","title":{"rendered":"M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh led t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c th\u00f4ng minh b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 m\u1eaft ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i n\u0103m, khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c th\u00f4ng minh, nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p d\u1ea1y h\u1ecdc kh\u00e1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111ang ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n, b\u1ea3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u \u201cch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng\u201d trong c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh led t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c th\u00f4ng minh.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4876 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"457\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ednh n\u0103ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi b\u1ea3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c nh\u01b0:<\/p>\n<p>&#8211; C\u1ea5u t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh led t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c th\u00f4ng minh \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n h\u01a1n b\u1ea3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c th\u00f4ng minh.<\/p>\n<p>&#8211; Ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tuy\u1ec7t h\u1ea3o, nhi\u1ec1u k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1eeb Full HD \u0111\u1ebfn Ultra HD 4K.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4877 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"546\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p>&#8211; C\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng m\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ebfn 20 \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi tr\u00ean c\u00f9ng 1 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4878 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"403\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p>&#8211; Tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn cao h\u01a1n b\u1ea3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n, ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec7n n\u0103ng h\u01a1n\u2026 th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh led t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c thay cho b\u1ea3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c c\u00f2n \u0111em l\u1ea1i cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe t\u1ed1t.<\/p>\n<p>M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c th\u00f4ng minh hi\u1ec7n nay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe cho \u0111\u00f4i m\u1eaft ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng nh\u01b0: C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ch\u1ed1ng ch\u00f3i, c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf nh\u00e1y m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh, c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 l\u1ecdc \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng xanh, \u2026<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4880 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"484\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t\u00a0 trong nh\u01b0ng \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh led t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c th\u00f4ng minh so v\u1edbi b\u1ea3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c. S\u1ef1 ra \u0111\u1eddi c\u1ee7a m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh led t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c th\u00f4ng minh \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0m ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n ti\u00eau ch\u00ed: gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng \u2013 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i n\u0103m, khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c th\u00f4ng minh, nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p d\u1ea1y h\u1ecdc kh\u00e1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111ang ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n, b\u1ea3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u \u201cch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng\u201d trong c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":9133,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[66],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4875","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tin-tuc"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4875","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4875"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4875\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":9134,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4875\/revisions\/9134"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/9133"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.c